title: Why You Should Move Away from Home - pros and cons
description: Hello everyone! In today's episode, I will be sharing all the reasons why I decided to move away from home, how the opportunity came about, how I had that conversation with my parents, and how my experience was, overall. There were definitely big pros and cons. With everything that I share, I hope that this episode can provide a bit of clarity. Stay happy and healthy!  --- Send in a voice message: https://anchor.fm/happyandhealthy/message Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/happyandhealthy/support
